posting_body: ['25102 62nd Avenue South, Kent, WA 98032', 'Signature Pointe Apartments lies alongside the Green River in Kent and is surrounded by tall evergreen trees.', 'The community offers many amenities for residents to enjoy year-round, from outdoor tennis courts, playgrounds, and fire pits, to indoor fitness centers and pools.', "You'll always find something to keep you busy here at Signature Pointe.", 'Apartment Features:', 'Top Floor Units Feature 19-ft Ceilings', 'Double Sinks', 'Separate Dining Room', 'Wood Burning Fireplace', 'Built-In Bookshelves', 'Full-Size Washer/Dryer', 'Community Features:', 'Views of Mount Rainier', 'Heated Indoor Pool, Sauna, & Spa', 'Adjacent to Riverbend Golf Course', 'Outdoor BBQs & Firepits', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Garages & Carports Available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
